summary: An Ordinance providing for the improvement of Occidental Avenue, from Connecticut Street to Holgate Street; and Atlantic Street, and Massachusetts Street, each from Occidental Avenue to First Avenue South, all in The City of Seattle, by filling the same, in accordance with Resolution No. 1505 of the City Council of the City of Seattle, and providing for the payment therefor by the mode of "Payment by Bonds," as provided by the laws of the State of Washington and the Charter and Ordinances of the City of Seattle
